Privacy Policy for Irene's Diary Dating App

Introduction

At Irene's Diary, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our dating app and services provided by our real human matchmakers. We only collect the minimum amount of personal information necessary to provide you with a safe and enjoyable experience on our platform.

Information Collection and Use

We collect your phone number when you sign up for an account with Irene's Diary. This phone number is used to verify your identity and to provide you with access to our services. We may also use your phone number to contact you with important information about your account or to notify you of updates to our app or services.

We do not collect any other personal information, such as your name, address, or email. However, when you use our matchmaking services, you may be asked to provide additional information about yourself to help our matchmaker to find the best match for you. This information will be kept strictly confidential and will only be shared with the matchmaker assigned to you.

Information Sharing and Disclosure

We do not share or disclose any of your personal information to third parties, except as required by law or in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to comply with a legal obligation or protect the rights or safety of Irene's Diary, its users, or the public.

Data Retention and Security

We take the security of your personal information very seriously and have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Changes to Our Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or to comply with legal or regulatory requirements. If we make any material changes, we will notify you by email or by posting a notice on our app.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, or if you wish to exercise any of your rights under this policy, please contact us at irenesdiary.tz@gmail.com

By using Irene's Diary, you consent to the collection, use, and sharing of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy.
